{"tid":964714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"誤播成龍床上戲　伊朗電視台負責人被炒","createTime":"2019-01-01T13:52:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-01T14:06:12.000Z","uid":39464,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"24c735665356ca0ff87d66f476e9487eba730eb3","tid":964714,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T13:52:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/jackie_QqNMS_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fjackie_QqNMS_1200x0.png&h=4db5889a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n伊朗國營電視台IRIB旗下的一個電視頻道，早前播出成龍電影作品《新宿事件》，期間未有將成龍的床上戲剪走，違反了當地嚴謹的廣播審查規定。事件導致該地區電視頻道的負責人被解僱。<br />\n<br />\n網上流傳的一段影片可見，伊朗南部基什島的觀眾，可以收看到當地電視台播出《新宿事件》，戲中成龍正與另一名女演員親熱。當地媒體形容，電視台是徹底違反IRIB的規則，播出了這一幕「不道德」的場面。<br />\n<br />\n當地媒體指，該地區電視頻道的負責人，連同多名電視台員工均已被解僱。而IRIB負責人Aliasgari Ali Askari已下令針對事件展開調查，承諾會認真對待違法者，並向有關當局報告。<br />\n<br />\n在伊朗，電視不能播放男女之間的身體接觸，以及男女之間溫柔的言辭或笑話。女性面孔的大特寫，又或是針對警察的負面描繪等畫面，同樣要被審查剪走。<br />\n<br />\n有部分網民就質疑IRIB反應過度敏感，反諷上周當地發生的致命交通意外都沒有官員要辭職，「公共汽車翻側、飛機墜毀、船隻沉沒&hellip;&hellip;都沒有人被解僱&hellip;&hellip;成龍在IRIB上做愛幾秒鐘，所有相關工作人員都被解僱了」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E8%AA%A4%E6%92%AD%E6%88%90%E9%BE%8D%E5%BA%8A%E4%B8%8A%E6%88%B2-%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E5%8F%B0%E8%B2%A0%E8%B2%AC%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E7%82%92/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E6%2592%25AD%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%25BE%258D%25E5%25BA%258A%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%2588%25B2-%25E4%25BC%258A%25E6%259C%2597%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%258F%25B0%25E8%25B2%25A0%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%2582%2592%2F&d=uqPq7KTnenMUT4vIE0AL0f755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=aa4ddfff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E6%2592%25AD%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%25BE%258D%25E5%25BA%258A%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%2588%25B2-%25E4%25BC%258A%25E6%259C%2597%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%258F%25B0%25E8%25B2%25A0%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%2582%2592%2F&h=761fcc89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E8%AA%A4%E6%92%AD%E6%88%90%E9%BE%8D%E5%BA%8A%E4%B8%8A%E6%88%B2-%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E5%8F%B0%E8%B2%A0%E8%B2%AC%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E7%82%92/</a>"},{"pid":"1f1480b66752bb4b7ca1cbd486a184a98aa0892b","tid":964714,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T13:54:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"71693c1086db75a2b77e79e4ef124e224565ecbc","tid":964714,"uid":220701,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1f1480b66752bb4b7ca1cbd486a184a98aa0892b","tid":964714,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T13:54:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T13:55:24.000Z","msg":"做夠假膠未"},{"pid":"530789c6b43ce395329f66a3beaaf8ae5f767330","tid":964714,"uid":25641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T14:00:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"390a936adaf3446239553b7e103816cf81cdd2ba","tid":964714,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T14:00:27.000Z","msg":"精神勝利法：伊朗播成龍電影，反映強國「一帶一路」成功？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e25a8b5d5bfe01f6b40076457bb754970c0c2ef","tid":964714,"uid":208159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T14:06:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}